# ─── CSC / CSC2 (Colesurfs Correction) — training archive & model artifacts ───
# All of these are local-only data stores. They accumulate historical and live
# forecast cycles, buoy observations, and trained model weights. None of it
# belongs in Git: it's large, grows continuously, and is reproducible from
# the public sources the backfills pull from (GEE, AWS noaa-gfs-bdp-pds, NDBC).
